headline: Southern Company Pledges Steady Customer Rates Through 2027
summary: SO's subsidiary Alabama Power commits to steady rates through 2027 while strengthening the grid and offering tools to help households manage monthly bills.

headline: Is Dominion Energy Stock Underperforming the S&P 500?
summary: As Dominion Energy has lagged behind the S&P 500 Index over the past year, analysts are cautious about the stock’s prospects.
